description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you an enthusiastic, inspirational and assertive nurse with a passion for ensuring high quality of care, safe services with excellent outcomes? An exciting development opportunity has arisen for a District Nurse Team Leader within the Vale Locality . You will provide strong clinical leadership to a District Nursing Team as well as having operational responsibility for the delivery of key performance outcomes, patient safety, clinical governance and regulatory compliance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an innovative, motivated, experienced nurse with excellent communication skills, passionate about promoting a culture of learning and sharing good practice. Committed to patient experience, staff development and service improvement. If you are, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 12/11/2020 &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Kate Roberts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Senior Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: kate.roberts@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 07976050099 &lt;/p&gt;
